{"tid":347822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺香港人玩meme方式好易令人煩厭","createTime":"2017-08-05T07:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T13:33:13.000Z","uid":93141,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28daad560202b9da210a468debd5e4cd2efed5d4","tid":347822,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:12:33.000Z","msg":"係咪因為香港人鍾意過度使用同一個meme同埋傳媒得個抄字,搞到玩到爛曬都唔肯收手,更莫講有班人玩得特別慢跟唔上潮流,睇到佢地講都好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如最近freestyle,三七氣流,阿嬌金句etc,一比毛記掂一掂就即刻成班人一直講講講,原本好笑既最後日提夜提都係同一個meme,你唔煩我都厭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dba3944aa24e74eaa20f2ab687db395e0b20b8f","tid":347822,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"補充一點,零創作性應該係香港人玩meme最失敗既一點,淨識一直quote最原先既野而冇新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb907024ebd2e1006c5f669041d22b2e308a426c","tid":347822,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7b6327d0e85f76b333358695389c7b86657967","tid":347822,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"香港啲meme都玩唔長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一過左潮流就已經唔會記得"},{"pid":"7b70b8ecbe1ad0c14d6256f9a33ac75f070ab6eb","tid":347822,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港啲meme都玩唔長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一過左潮流就已經唔會記得</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係chur盡曬,之後再見到就會反感<br />\n同埋歐美可能人口多,個創造性就大好多,一個meme改少少又可以笑多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8986ceb92c82726314687776269d14b12b751a0a","tid":347822,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ada04dcc0db5c9f37c31673f5440feabb4e295","tid":347822,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}